{"tid":438032,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"沖涼液加水 正唔正常","createTime":"2017-10-16T13:53:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T15:11:41.000Z","uid":141987,"like":71,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5b3ee7f8e3ebbc32da7587705bcdc3b8a5e2a7ec","tid":438032,"uid":141987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:53:55.000Z","msg":"我老母就係咁 將d沖涼液、洗手液用完竟然加水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要加成枝水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到我用到勁稀，返屋企洗手永遠覺得唔夠消毒<br />\n到底咁樣正唔正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔正常囉，加咁多水點用<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  下 好正常，唔加好浪費！"},{"pid":"feac7f54ebc38faa448fcfc20396fb33e2d7786d","tid":438032,"uid":21423,"like":10,"dislike":7,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:54:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43da9642c20cf68f6ddf35f19aa6ac38dd1124d8","tid":438032,"uid":141987,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:55:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常，雪凍嚟飲好解渴</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a52fa54d3277a65b95a3a509ce17866aa0b70221","tid":438032,"uid":22947,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:55:58.000Z","msg":"窮西行為"},{"pid":"cfe4d868efefb1060e3d5d95e0ecae8b318a8437","tid":438032,"uid":57062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:58:40.000Z","msg":"屌 我屋企都係會咁"},{"pid":"6944dc468668cf8010b24d901490d998be3e4c2c","tid":438032,"uid":141987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:59:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 我屋企都係會咁</blockquote><br />\n激撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好慳唔慳，慳係個幾滴沖涼液到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2d4b2703c61687555fe21a169b963580f2f0a8","tid":438032,"uid":52942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:00:24.000Z","msg":"用到冇哂又唔記得買先會咁"},{"pid":"c6f59e6dcb02fa98cb3d54181b563964357073e9","tid":438032,"uid":36478,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:11:48.000Z","msg":"其實開個蓋倒出嚟都用得<br />\n何必要加水呢"},{"pid":"1d28ee2db9cba1099ca5f26d0d579d4de88a45a2","tid":438032,"uid":142532,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:14:27.000Z","msg":"老母就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />專慳d九唔搭八既野<br />\n試過明明屋企有幾個月垃圾袋未拎<br />\n都仲要搵個濕鳩金象米袋黎鋪垃圾筒"},{"pid":"e73b1344abdc3e51cf031bedb4e8c0f9e91fa5b1","tid":438032,"uid":29312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:18:31.000Z","msg":"我老母又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用到得返小小就開始加水 噴出黎啲沖涼液跟本水黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  所以一見佢咁做就自動買支新既  支沖涼水比佢自己用飽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e9e1a72ba720a196d3047e4e2b7956c412e6987","tid":438032,"uid":141987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:44:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我老母又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用到得返小小就開始加水 噴出黎啲沖涼液跟本水黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  所以一見佢咁做就自動買支新既  支沖涼水比佢自己用飽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好搞笑，我依家都係自己開枝新，留返枝沖涼水比佢自己用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee07ed6e38b6261d345cd23ad5ae205bc9d20b36","tid":438032,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:48:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0284e963860b36f15824ea82c41ac598ef78f8c","tid":438032,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:49:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ffd6ab50aec6945116dd47760e0ce50a71d79ee4","tid":438032,"uid":55937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:50:38.000Z","msg":"用曬每日都唔記得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加水用好過唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c6aa53310c2bf02aea563e964fb1b4be87824e","tid":438032,"uid":49477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:54:32.000Z","msg":"我老母都係咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a78152b8030a78f8533cbccd7de528ebfdb5c527","tid":438032,"uid":11161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻倒撚晒佢  溝溝溝 咁鐘意溝<br />\n以後唔洗煲湯 飲滾水得啦"},{"pid":"09db3642c9d569df063306995aaa8cbee034acae","tid":438032,"uid":141987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:57:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻倒撚晒佢  溝溝溝 咁鐘意溝<br />\n以後唔洗煲湯 飲滾水得啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都係一個方法，直頭幫佢倒左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  等佢加都無得加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3185d9c5272a1187a9598d0f6668c323e4e4f83","tid":438032,"uid":31031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:00:46.000Z","msg":"加少少水用埋淨低嗰d都正常 但真係少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6df40df957505981f3fb050b6754ea2e7348508","tid":438032,"uid":39885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:04:21.000Z","msg":"聽講解決方法就係趁佢只加少少水溝果陣<br />\n成枝「沖涼水」倒落身到用左佢<br />\n廢事淨返少少水又繼續畀佢溝落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過你個case一黎就加到成枝都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ⋯⋯"},{"pid":"74ab68568ef6dea5b6825bd7e0e504e38217641d","tid":438032,"uid":50801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:09:26.000Z","msg":"倒晒支沖涼水再用水喉水&ldquo;浪&rdquo;到個樽乾乾淨淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596393f2f93b7c86ae8ede326411a62517a7d0d4","tid":438032,"uid":129013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:11:41.000Z","msg":"加太多又係over左嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}